description: The TRANSFORMERS Animated Series takes the concept of ROBOTS IN DISGUISE and reinvents it for an all-new generation of fans! And now the animated shows can be enjoyed in print, too—in the form of all-new books that use actual still frames from the new animated series to offer a unique reading experience for TRANSFORMERS fans of all ages. This first volume contains the entire 70-minute kick-off adventure!

description: In this second volume of the TRANSFORMERS ANIMATED SERIES, TRANSFORMERS fans can experience two complete episodes of the all-new animated series. The TRANSFORMERS have come to New Detroit, and nothing will ever be the same again! Volume two contains two stand-alone episodes of this exciting new show.

name: The Island of Death

description: released on september 1995

Dr.Grave and Shandar in "Satan's Fury: Part One: The Brotherhood of Doom"

The two‘heroes’ set off to Egypt where they are attempting to steal the Heart of

Osiris off Rama who intends to use the ancient jewel for some ‘villainous

purpose’ (but really Dr.Grave just wants to sell it at auction). Having lost

the jewel in a fight, Shandar and Dr.Grave steal the ceremonial altar instead.

The next story sees Shandar and Dr.Grave go to Austria to exorcise a demon who is

terrorising Wiener Monastery. We find out that shandar is dr.graves man-servant

because he was saved by him many years ago and owes his life to him entirely.

We also find out that Dr.Grave was a minister but became prey to the master of

darkness and vowed from that day on to combat the devils work, in whatever form

it took. After ‘exorcising’ the demon of the ‘Monastery by shooting it in the

face, Shandar and Dr.Grave must now find the mysterious Circle of Power in

order to save the others of Wiener Monstery...
name: Dr.Grave

description:
Dr.Grave and Shandar “Satan’s Fury: Part Three: Episode Two: That Furious Satan”

Dr.Grave meets the Grim Reaper and comes to his rightful place in Heaven but he is soon

sent back to earth to face some unfinished business...
name: Dr.Grave

description:
Dr.Grave and Shandar in “The Curse of Zombina”

Anabelle Le Blanche aka Zombina is back to wreak havoc once again with her seductive

prowess, she is on a mission to make Zombie’s of all the men of New Orleans,

can our heroes to stop her...?
name: Dr.Grave
